      "text": "よく似合ってるよ。毎回思うが、もし恋のプロモは\n衣装までこだわっているよな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It looks good on you. I think about it every time‚ but they’re really\nparticular about outfits for the MoshiKoi promos.",
