      "text": "ああ、そうだな。ゲームが好評だったからだろう\n事務所に届いてる感想も読んだか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ you’re right. That must be because the game has been well-received.\nHave you read the impressions that have been sent to the office?",
